# MauriMesh Raw-Device Evidence Run Kit

## Purpose

This kit captures stronger live-device evidence from A06, S10, and A16.

It records:

- Raw ADB/logcat from every connected device.
- Device properties.
- Battery, Wi-Fi, and Bluetooth dumps.
- Before and after screenshots.
- Screenrecording from each device.
- Filtered MauriMesh proof logs.
- SHA-256 file hash list.
- Verification report.

## Important

Install this kit in Replit/project root.

Run the live capture on the Mac terminal where ADB can see the physical phones.

## Mac Capture Command

From project root on your Mac:

```bash
chmod +x tools/raw-evidence/capture-maurimesh-raw-device-evidence.sh
DURATION=240 ./tools/raw-evidence/capture-maurimesh-raw-device-evidence.sh
